text: Darwin Piñeyrúa was a athlete from Uruguay. Piñeyrúa competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics. He was born on 23 December 1945 and died on 11 February 1978.Darwin Piñeyrúa == References == Category:1945 births Category:1978 deaths Category:Uruguayan athletes Category:Hammer throwers Category:Olympians for Uruguay Category:Sportspeople from Montevideo
